I am Ouadi Maakoul. My background bridges the domains this book covers: artificial intelligence, autonomous systems, and space technologies. I have spent my career at the intersection of software and systems that operate without direct human control—first in academic research, later in industry deployment, and now as an observer of the global AI landscape from my base in Rabat, Morocco.

